.Dd June 18, 2005
.Dt CENTRAL 4 sparc64
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm central
.Nd "Central host controller and bus"
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "device central"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for the
.Tn Central
host controller and bus found in
.Tn Sun Enterprise xx00
systems.
It provides an attachment point for the main
.Xr fhc 4
.Tn FireHose
controller used to control board level functions on the host.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr fhc 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver first appeared in
.Fx 5.1 .
.Sh AUTHORS
The
.Nm
driver was written by
.An Jake Burkholder Aq Mt jake@FreeBSD.org .
